{"lemma":"مَكْتَبَيْ","slug":"مَكْتَبَيْ","root":"ك.ت.ب","root_slug":"ك-ت-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ت-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36640","n36641","n36642","n36644"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"maktab, elementary school","tags":["historical"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"desk"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"office"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bureau"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"study"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the root ك ت ب (k t b)."},"ipa":["/mak.tab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36640","headword_ar":"مَكْتَبٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kut~aAbN","text_ar":"كُتَّابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, &c.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A school; a place where the art of writing is taught:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.:) accord. to Mbr and F, the assigning this signification to the latter word is an error; it being a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAtibN","text_ar":"كَاتِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and signifying, accord. to Mbr, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boys of a school:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the A it is said, this word is said to signify the boys; not the place: but Esh-Shiháb says, in the Sharh esh-Shifa, that it occurs in this sense in the classical language, and is not to be regarded as a postclassical word: it is said to be originally a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAtibN","text_ar":"كَاتِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and to be fig. employed to signify a school. (TA.) Pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makaAtibu","text_ar":"مَكَاتِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataAtiybu","text_ar":"كَتَاتِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n36641","headword_ar":"مُكْتَبٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katiybN","text_ar":"كَتِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36642","headword_ar":"مُكْتِبٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A teacher of the art of writing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36644","headword_ar":"مُكَتَّبٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A bunch of grapes and the like"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which a part has been eaten."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}